00:56:36,476 --> 00:56:39,312
Kimchi ini sangat sedap.

707
00:56:39,396 --> 00:56:41,940
Rasanya menyegarkan, bukan?

708
00:56:42,023 --> 00:56:43,233
Ya.

709
00:56:43,316 --> 00:56:44,776
Nah, makan lagi.

710
00:56:44,859 --> 00:56:46,361
Terima kasih.

711
00:56:48,863 --> 00:56:51,533
Perlahan-lahan.
